      <file>.claude/constraints/bff-extensions.md</file>
      <file>.claude/patterns/api/endpoint-definition.md</file>
    </files>
  </knowledge>

  <steps>
    <step order="1">Read `Sprk.Bff.Api/Options/WorkspaceOptions.cs` — note existing properties (esp. `SummarizePlaybookId` GUID).</step>
    <step order="2">Add `public string SummarizePlaybookCode { get; set; } = string.Empty;` to `WorkspaceOptions` with XML doc comment referencing FR-04.</step>
    <step order="3">Verify `WorkspaceOptions` is registered via `services.Configure&lt;WorkspaceOptions&gt;(config.GetSection("Workspace"))` in `Program.cs` or a module file. Add if missing.</step>
    <step order="4">Read `WorkspaceFileEndpoints.cs:30,254`. Replace `IConfiguration["Workspace:SummarizePlaybookId"]` indexer reads with `IOptions&lt;WorkspaceOptions&gt;.Value.SummarizePlaybookId` (existing GUID property — backward-compat preserved).</step>
    <step order="5">Add `IOptions&lt;WorkspaceOptions&gt;` to the endpoint handler signature; remove the raw `IConfiguration` injection if no longer used.</step>
    <step order="6">Update `appsettings.Development.json` (or relevant config file) — add `Workspace:SummarizePlaybookCode = "summarize-document-workspace"` so task 019 can consume it.</step>
    <step order="7">Add unit test in `tests/unit/Sprk.Bff.Api.Tests/Options/WorkspaceOptionsTests.cs` asserting `SummarizePlaybookCode` binds correctly from config section.</step>
    <step order="8">Run `dotnet build src/server/api/Sprk.Bff.Api/` + `dotnet test tests/unit/Sprk.Bff.Api.Tests/` — pass.</step>
    <step order="9">Measure publish size; report delta.</step>
    <step order="10">Run code-review + adr-check (Step 9.5 FULL gates).</step>
    <step order="11">Update TASK-INDEX.md: task 012 → ✅.</step>
  </steps>

  <tools>
    <tool name="Read">WorkspaceOptions.cs + WorkspaceFileEndpoints.cs</tool>
    <tool name="Edit">Modify options + endpoint + config + add test</tool>
    <tool name="Bash">dotnet build / test / publish</tool>
    <tool name="Grep">Verify zero `IConfiguration["Workspace:SummarizePlaybookId"]` remains</tool>
  </tools>

